# Smart Health Monitoring with AI & IoT

## üìå Overview
The **Smart Health Monitoring System** leverages **IoT devices** and **AI (gpt-oss model)** to provide real-time health insights, anomaly detection, and personalized wellness recommendations.  
It enables continuous monitoring of vital signs, early detection of risks, and remote access for doctors and family members.

---

## üöÄ Features
- Real-time health data collection (heart rate, SpO‚ÇÇ, BP, sleep patterns).  
- AI-powered insights using the **gpt-oss model**.  
- Alerts for anomalies and emergencies.  
- Personalized lifestyle and wellness suggestions.  
- Cloud-based storage with secure access.  
- Multi-user and family health dashboard.  

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack
- **IoT Devices:** Arduino / ESP32 / Smartwatch Sensors (C++, MicroPython)  
- **Backend:** Python (Flask/FastAPI), Node.js  
- **AI/ML:** Python (TensorFlow, PyTorch, scikit-learn, gpt-oss)  
- **Frontend:** React.js (web) / Flutter (mobile)  
- **Database:** Firebase (real-time), PostgreSQL (structured storage)  
- **Protocols:** MQTT, REST APIs  

